headline.main: Questions for: ‘Before Vaquitas Vanish, a Desperate Bid to Save Them’
headline.print_headline: Questions for: ‘Before Vaquitas Vanish, a Desperate Bid to Save Them’

lead_paragraph: The Kurdish-led administration in northeastern Syria says a new land corridor to the government-controlled west marks an economic breakthrough for their autonomous region that has been under "siege" by hostile parties.
